%% ====================================================================
%% Sequence 02: Task Creation (due date required, visibility, stakeholders)
%% Task Management System v1.2
%% ====================================================================
sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor User as ユーザー (所有者)
  participant Browser as ブラウザ
  participant Sec as Spring Security<br/>(OAuth2 RS)
  participant Filter as TenantContextFilter
  participant Ctrl as TaskController<br/>(adapter.web)
  participant UC as CreateTaskUseCase<br/>(usecase.task)
  participant Domain as Task / DomainService<br/>(domain)
  participant TaskRepo as TaskRepositoryImpl<br/>(adapter.persistence)
  participant SHRepo as StakeholderRepositoryImpl
  participant Audit as AuditLogger
  participant DB as MySQL

  User->>Browser: 期限必須フォーム入力<br/>(public=STAKEHOLDERS、関係者2名指定)
  Browser->>Sec: POST /api/tasks<br/>Authorization: Bearer JWT<br/>X-Tenant-Id: 11
  Sec->>Sec: JWT署名検証 + クレーム抽出
  Sec->>Filter: 認証済 Principal を渡す
  Filter->>Filter: TenantContext.set(tenantId=11, userId=1, role=MEMBER)<br/>(以降のSQLにHibernate Filterで自動付与)
  Filter->>Ctrl: forward
  Ctrl->>Ctrl: @Valid TaskCreateRequest (Bean Validation)<br/>title必須, dueDate必須, priority必須, visibility必須
  Ctrl->>UC: execute(CreateTaskCommand)

  UC->>UC: ownerId, tenantId は ActorContext から自動取得<br/>(リクエストボディは無視)
  UC->>Domain: new Task(title, dueDate, priority, visibility, ownerId, ...)
  Domain->>Domain: 不変条件チェック<br/>(dueDate≠null, title 1..100文字)
  Domain-->>UC: Task インスタンス

  alt visibility = STAKEHOLDERS
    UC->>UC: stakeholderUserIds 検証<br/>(同テナント内の有効ユーザーか)
  else
    Note over UC: stakeholders は無視
  end

  UC->>TaskRepo: save(task)
  TaskRepo->>DB: INSERT INTO tasks<br/>(tenant_id, owner_id, title, due_date, priority, visibility, ...)
  DB-->>TaskRepo: id=101
  alt visibility = STAKEHOLDERS
    UC->>SHRepo: replaceAll(taskId=101, [3, 5], addedBy=1)
    SHRepo->>DB: INSERT task_stakeholders ×2
  end

  UC->>Audit: log(CREATE_TASK, actor, taskId=101, diff)
  Audit->>DB: INSERT audit_logs (hash_chain = SHA256(prev || payload))

  UC-->>Ctrl: Task
  Ctrl-->>Browser: 201 Created + Task JSON
  Browser-->>User: 一覧画面へ遷移 (新規タスクが当日セクションに表示)

  Note over Filter,DB: テナント分離: 全SQLに WHERE tenant_id=11 が<br/>Hibernate Filterによって自動付与される
